remarks: Membership in a left open, right closed interval.  (Contributed by Glauco Siliprandi, 11-Dec-2019.)
statement:
eliocd.a $e |- ( ph -> A e. RR* ) $.
eliocd.b $e |- ( ph -> B e. RR* ) $.
eliocd.c $e |- ( ph -> C e. RR* ) $.
eliocd.altc $e |- ( ph -> A < C ) $.
eliocd.cleb $e |- ( ph -> C <_ B ) $.
eliocd $p |- ( ph -> C e. ( A (,] B ) ) $.
